sequenceDiagram
    participant C1 as Client (Device 1)
    participant Meta as Metadata Service
    participant Block as Block Service
    participant Notify as Notify Service
    participant C2 as Client (Device 2)

    Note over C1,Block: UPLOAD (chunk-based dedup)
    C1->>C1: split file into 4MB chunks, SHA-256 each
    C1->>Meta: POST /file {metadata, chunk_hashes[]}
    Meta->>Meta: check ref-counts for each hash
    Meta-->>C1: {file_id, missing_chunks: [hash...]}
    loop only missing chunks
        C1->>Block: PUT /chunk/{hash} bytes
        Block-->>C1: stored
    end
    C1->>Meta: finalize version
    Meta->>Meta: bump current_version, incr ref_counts
    Meta-->>C1: version_id committed
    Meta-)Notify: file_changed event

    Note over Notify,C2: SYNC TO OTHER DEVICE
    Notify-)C2: WS {event: file_changed, file_id, version}
    C2->>Meta: GET /file/{id}
    Meta-->>C2: metadata + chunk_list
    C2->>C2: diff vs local chunks
    loop missing chunks only
        C2->>Block: GET /chunk/{hash}
        Block-->>C2: bytes (CDN)
    end
    C2->>C2: reassemble file locally
